==English==

===Etymology===
From Old Norse [[nigla]].

===Adjective===
'''niggardly'''

# [[miserly]], [[stingy]].

====Usage notes====
Some people irrationally feel this term to be offensive, due to it sounding similar to the term [[nigger]], although etymologically the two words have nothing to do with each other. See [[Wikipedia:Niggardly]].

